OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,FA village has come together in support
OL,8,Fof a family after they lost everything
OL,9,Fin a house fire.
OL,11,FKim Leighton and her son Cole, 11,
OL,12,Fsuffered serious burn injuries after
OL,13,Fthe blaze at their home, in Clayton
OL,14,FGreen, near Chorley, just before
OL,15,Fmidnight on 6 January, and are both in
OL,16,Fa critical condition in hospital.
OL,18,FFour other members of their family -
OL,19,Faged nine, 13, 18 and 45 - were taken
OL,20,Fto hospital but have now been
OL,21,Fdischarged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
