OL,7,FFollowing the fire the local community
OL,8,Frallied around the family, and an
OL,9,Fonline fundraiser has already secured
OL,10,Fmore than #20,000 of their #60,000
OL,11,Ftarget.
OL,13,FNeighbour Mitch Thomas, who set up the
OL,14,Ffundraiser and helped the family on
OL,15,Fthe night, said: "You could see the
OL,16,Fflames coming out of the windows and
OL,17,Fthe sides. It was already quite severe
OL,18,Fat that point.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
