OL,7,F"As it developed and got worse, it was
OL,8,Fa bit like a furnace. It was roaring
OL,9,Fangry flames, a lot of smoke and
OL,10,Fthings popping and banging inside. It
OL,11,Fwas aggressive.
OL,13,F"Everything's gone unfortunately.
OL,14,FWe're not able to go in to have a look
OL,15,Fbut from what we can see from the
OL,16,Foutside, the whole top floor has gone
OL,17,Fthere's nothing left, it's more like a
OL,18,Fwreckage yard in there."
