OL,7,FPolice say the cause of the fire is
OL,8,F"subject to a joint investigation
OL,9,Fbetween police and the fire service,
OL,10,Fand enquiries are ongoing".
OL,12,FIn the immediate aftermath, neighbours
OL,13,Fcame to the support of the family,
OL,14,Fwith people offering first aid and
OL,15,Finviting those who were not injured
OL,16,Finto their house.
