OL,7,FSince then, people have donated
OL,8,Fclothes, furniture and household
OL,9,Fappliances, while others have offered
OL,10,Fservices such as storage units and
OL,11,Fcooked meals.
OL,13,F"It's been unbelievable", Mitch said
OL,14,Fof the community effort. "People have
OL,15,Fbeen offering services, cooking meals
OL,16,Ffor the kids, giving them school
OL,17,Funiform, offering them a lift to
OL,18,Fschool.
OL,20,F"We've just been inundated with people
OL,21,Fbuying new things."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
