OL,7,FAt a storage unit at Botany Bay,
OL,8,Fneighbours and family friends have
OL,9,Fbeen sorting through donations that
OL,10,Fhave been made.
OL,12,FEven the storage unit itself is a
OL,13,Fdonation made by Chris Hickman from
OL,14,FCuboid Self Storage, who is friends
OL,15,Fwith the family.
OL,17,FHe said: "It's completely devastating
OL,18,Fto a family who's well known
OL,19,Fthroughout Chorley and we wanted to
OL,20,Fhelp as much as possible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
