OL,5,Cfire
OL,7,F"We were aware that a lot of people
OL,8,Fwanted to donate furniture to help the
OL,9,Ffamily rebuild their lives and they
OL,10,Fneeded somewhere to put it.
OL,12,F"It's the least that we can do. We are
OL,13,Fgoing to hold onto the items and store
OL,14,Fit until the family are ready for it.
OL,16,F"We're getting phone calls all the
OL,17,Ftime, the community has really pulled
OL,18,Ftogether for one of their own. It's
OL,19,Famazing to see."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
