OL,7,FIn a statement, Lancashire Police
OL,8,Fsaid: "We were called by Lancashire
OL,9,FFire and Rescue Service at 11.58pm on
OL,10,F6th January to a report of a fire at a
OL,11,Fhouse in Greenwood, Clayton Green.
OL,13,F"The emergency services attended and
OL,14,Fcolleagues from LFRS extinguished the
OL,15,Ffire.
OL,17,F"A boy, aged 11, suffered serious burn
OL,18,Finjuries and was taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwhere he is in a critical condition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
